categories: Category:Grand Army of the Republic units

nodes.text: A unit within the Grand Army of the Republic led by Jedi General Quinlan Vos was active during the Clone Wars between the Galactic Republic and the Separatist Alliance after Vos's return to the light side of the Force after his assassination attempt on Separatist leader Count Dooku failed. The unit participated in one of the longest-lasting campaigns of the Outer Rim Sieges in order to defend the planet Saleucami. After the Siege of Saleucami, Vos and his troops were needed on Boz Pity where they emerged victorious.
